            notehtml += '<p>The scan determined that the following items have date restrictions set outside the current <strong>Course Start Date</strong> and <strong>Course End Date</strong>.</p>';
            notehtml += '<div class="table-responsive-sm"><table id="table-course-dates" class="table"><tbody><tr><td>Start Date</td><td>'+csdate_display+'</td></tr><tr><td>End Date</td><td>'+cedate_display+'</td></tr></tbody></table></div>';
            notehtml += '<p>You can review this date range by going to Course Admin > Course Offering Information.</p>'
